name: A Creators Tale - Wealth Creation
description:
There will be only one creation of this piece. If it is now yours, Congratulations. There is only one commitment required and that is that you pass it on once this particular journey or obstacle has been overcome for you.
In order to create wealth in your life it is important to break all negative bonds and associations with it. Money is an illusion. Wealth is not. Today you speak into existence overflowing wealth in all areas. Health, love, finance. You have now realised it was all yours and there is no lack. No loss. This is your new truth.
Hold these words in your mind, heart and daily thoughts.
